OL,3,CStephen Flynn pledges to serve in
OL,4,Cwhatever capacity he is asked to by
OL,5,CSwinney
OL,7,FThe SNP's Westminster leader has
OL,8,Fpledged to serve however he is asked
OL,9,Fif he becomes an MSP next year.
OL,11,FStephen Flynn announced earlier this
OL,12,Fyear he would be seeking the Aberdeen
OL,13,FSouth seat ` the Holyrood equivalent
OL,14,Fof his constituency in the House of
OL,15,FCommons.
OL,17,FHe is widely seen as a potential
OL,18,Ffuture SNP leader and someone who will
OL,19,Flikely serve as a minister if the
OL,20,Fparty continues its near-two decade
OL,21,Fstint in power after May's election.
