OL,7,FBut speaking to the PA news agency, Mr
OL,8,FFlynn said he would do whatever job
OL,9,FFirst Minister John Swinney asks of
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,F"I will do whatever is asked of me by
OL,13,Fthe First Minister, irrespective of
OL,14,Fwhat that is," he said.
OL,16,F"If that is sitting on the back
OL,17,Fbenches and bringing some life to some
OL,18,Fof the debates in Holyrood, I'm up for
OL,19,Fthat.
