OL,7,F"If it's sitting on committees and
OL,8,Fscrutinising the work of the
OL,9,FGovernment, I think I'm relatively
OL,10,Feffective in that context.
OL,12,F"If it's sitting and engaging with
OL,13,F(journalists) to sell the message to
OL,14,Fthe people of Scotland, I'm quite
OL,15,Fhappy to do that as well."
OL,17,FThere is some "exceptional talent"
OL,18,Fstanding for the SNP next year, Mr
OL,19,FFlynn claimed, all of whom have a
OL,20,F"role to play".
