OL,7,FWhile Mr Flynn hopes to make it to
OL,8,FHolyrood next year, a number of very
OL,9,Fexperienced SNP MSPs ` including
OL,10,Fseveral ministers such as Deputy First
OL,11,FMinister Kate Forbes, Finance
OL,12,FSecretary Shona Robison and Transport
OL,13,FSecretary Fiona Hyslop ` have decided
OL,14,Fto step away.
OL,16,FBut despite vacancies around the
OL,17,FCabinet table, Mr Flynn refused to say
OL,18,Fif there were any jobs he had his eye
OL,19,Fon, sidestepping the question.
