OL,7,FHis comments come just over a week
OL,8,Fafter the SNP set its independence
OL,9,Fstrategy, making a majority for the
OL,10,Fparty next year the bar that would
OL,11,Fhave to be cleared before another
OL,12,Freferendum on separation can be sought.
OL,14,FBut failing to meet that target would
OL,15,Fundoubtedly see opposition MSPs urge
OL,16,Fthe SNP to shelve its independence
OL,17,Faspirations, regardless of if the
OL,18,Fparty is returned to government,
OL,19,Fsomething Mr Flynn said should spur on
OL,20,Fits supporters.
