OL,5,CSwinney
OL,7,F"What greater motivation could there
OL,8,Fbe for independence supporters in
OL,9,FScotland than to recognise how
OL,10,Fimportant that majority now is?" he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Now we need to get on and deliver it."
OL,15,FHe added: "I'm confident about our
OL,16,Fchances in that context... and we have
OL,17,Fto be confident.
