OL,7,F"We've got to sense that there's an
OL,8,Fenormous opportunity here to
OL,9,Fcompletely transform people's lives
OL,10,Fand to escape from what is broken,
OL,11,FBrexit Britain."
OL,13,FThe party's Westminster leader also
OL,14,Frejected assertions that the First
OL,15,FMinister's independence strategy was
OL,16,Fmade with the 2031 election in mind,
OL,17,Fsaying it was a "pitch to the public
OL,18,Ffor next year".
